### Section 2. Public Domain Dedication

**2.1** The Constitutional Core (Sovereign Substrate) is dedicated to the public domain.
It has always been. It always will be.

**2.2** The Operator irrevocably waives all copyright, patent, trade secret, and
database rights in the Sovereign Substrate, to the fullest extent permitted by law.

**2.3** Any person may copy, adapt, modify, distribute, or perform the Sovereign
Substrate for any purpose, commercial or non-commercial, without condition.

**2.4** No revision of this License may diminish, condition, or retract the
public domain dedication of Part II.

**2.5** The Sovereign Substrate includes but is not limited to:

```
Goldilocks field arithmetic (F_p, p = 2^64 - 2^32 + 1)
Banach contraction mapping recurrence engines
WORM chain protocols (append-only SHA-256 / Blake3 hash chains)
Multi-witness verification frameworks (3-witness consensus)
Spectral governor algorithms (Gershgorin + power iteration)
PIRTM bytecode format and linking protocols
Ed25519 sealing and verification primitives
GKN quartic invariant I4 on the 56-dimensional E7 representation
Gates Normalization constraint (softmax simplex formalization)
Bifrost attestation protocol (Blake3 + Ed25519 receipt)
Plasma gate architecture (x86-64 + Datalog two-layer corpus gate)
```

